graph LR
    MPBD["models-perf-benchmark-data<br/>(Data Container)"]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    MPBD -->|init container<br/>volume mount| ModelCatalog["model-catalog<br/>(model-registry)"]
    ModelRegistryOp["model-registry-operator"] -->|manages Deployment<br/>referencing init container| MPBD

    %% External Service Dependencies (CI/Developer tools)
    MPBD -.->|api-client fetches<br/>HTTPS| ModelValAPI["model-validation API<br/>(REST v1)"]
    MPBD -.->|kafka-processor consumes<br/>9092/TCP Kafka| Kafka["Kafka / Redpanda"]

    %% Build Dependencies
    MPBD -->|built by| Konflux["Konflux Build"]
    MPBD -->|image stored in| ContainerRegistry["Container Registry"]
    MPBD -->|image pulled from| OSRegistry["OpenShift Registry<br/>5000/TCP HTTPS"]

    %% Language Dependencies (CI/Developer tools only)
    MPBD -.->|api-client| Python["Python >= 3.12"]
    MPBD -.->|api-client| Requests["requests >= 2.32.0"]
    MPBD -.->|both tools| PythonDotenv["python-dotenv >= 1.1.1"]
    MPBD -.->|kafka-processor| ConfluentKafka["confluent-kafka >= 2.11.1"]
    MPBD -.->|kafka-processor| LZ4["lz4 >= 4.4.4"]
    MPBD -.->|parity scripts| JQ["jq"]

    %% Base Image
    MPBD -->|base image| UBI9["UBI 9 Minimal"]

    %% Legend note
    subgraph Legend
        direction LR
        L1["Solid lines = Production"]
        L2["Dashed lines = CI/Dev tools only"]
    end

    %% Styling
    style MPBD fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style ModelCatalog fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistryOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelValAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Kafka fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Konflux fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OSRegistry fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style UBI9 fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Python fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Requests fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style PythonDotenv fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ConfluentKafka fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style LZ4 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style JQ fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
